refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;

 boolsodium_crypto_aead_aes256gcm_is_available



 The return value of this function depends on whether or not the hardware supports hardware-accelerated AES.

&reftitle.changelog;





    &Version;
    &Description;





    8.4.0

     This function may now return &true; on aarch64 CPUs that provide the
     ARM cryptographic extensions (the ARMv8 AES instructions). Previously,
     hardware-accelerated AES-256-GCM was only detected on x86 and x86-64
     hardware, and this function always returned &false; on aarch64.
